item.description: 2nd Annual Plymouth Barktoberfest! Free to attend... The Plymouth Area Chamber of Commerce is happy to announce the return of Barktober-Fest! This family-friendly, pet-friendly event will take place again on Plymouth's historic waterfront. This event will feature pet-friendly vendors, food vendors, live entertainment, a pet costume contest and much more!... For more information, please call 508.830.1620 or email sarah@plymouthchamber.com... The NEBBC will most likely not have a booth at this event (as we have one at Woofstock in Sudbury on the same day), but we wanted to alert our Plymouth area members to this new event!
item.name: Barktoberfest in Plymouth, MA!
